description: The murmuring of the falls echoes from the east, mirroring the mellow babble of the northern river as it joins the eerie melody of nocturnal creatures rustling about the wilds.  Shadows cling to the densely clustered vines dangling from the sweeping branches of high-reaching trees, their leafy spirals swaying slowly in the occassional nighttime breeze.  Thin shafts of muted moonlight penetrate the hazy mist of the jungle canopy, creating wavering shadows that shift with each movement of limb or leaf.
title: [Saewehna Jungle, Wilds]
